SHUMWAY, Appellant, v. BELEY, Respondent. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fourth Department. May 18, 1894.) Action by Anna 0. Shumway against Fred Beley.

Argued before HARDIN, P. J., and MARTIN and VANN, JJ.

No opinion. Judgment of the county court reversed, with costs, and the judgment of the justice’s court affirmed, with costs.
